title: It's time to walk the dog...at Kidzmash...with a yo-yo

speakers.name: Connor Glenn
speakers.bio: Connor is a 5th grade student.  He loves playing chess, yo-yos, building Stem projects.  He wants to be a chef when he grows up.  He lives in Pennsylvania with Mom, Dad, sister, 2 dogs, 2 hermit crabs, and many fish.

excerpt: Yo-yos may be over 2000 years old but these tricks are trending.  Kidz will become hands on experts on how to preform basic yo-yo tricks (including walk the dog) then learn modern and complex maneuvers using their own yo-yo.
